## Implementation
- Use SafeAreaView for root-level screens or containers
- Apply useSafeAreaInsets() for manual inset management
- Use NativeWind's pt-safe and pb-safe for inset-aware padding
- Handle landscape and portrait orientations appropriately

## Device Compatibility
- Account for notches, dynamic islands, and rounded corners
- Test on different device sizes and orientations
- Ensure content remains accessible in all device states
